sequenceDiagram
    participant User as Data Scientist<br/>Notebook/KFP SDK
    participant Route as OpenShift Route<br/>ds-pipeline-{name}<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.2+
    participant OAuth as OAuth Proxy<br/>OpenShift Auth
    participant API as DS Pipeline API Server<br/>8888/TCP HTTP<br/>8887/TCP gRPC
    participant K8s as Kubernetes API<br/>6443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.2+
    participant Argo as Argo Workflow Controller<br/>Namespace-scoped
    participant WorkflowPod as Workflow Task Pod<br/>Ephemeral
    participant Storage as S3/Minio Storage<br/>9000/TCP HTTP or 443/TCP HTTPS
    participant DB as MariaDB<br/>3306/TCP MySQL
    participant MLMD as ML Metadata gRPC<br/>8080/TCP gRPC
    participant PersistAgent as Persistence Agent<br/>Metadata Tracker

    Note over User,DB: Flow 1: Pipeline Submission via API

    User->>Route: POST /apis/v2beta1/pipelines<br/>HTTPS 443<br/>Auth: OAuth Token
    Route->>OAuth: Validate OAuth Token<br/>TLS Termination
    OAuth->>API: Forward Request<br/>HTTP 8888<br/>Auth: Bearer Token
    API->>DB: Store Pipeline Metadata<br/>MySQL 3306<br/>Auth: Username/Password
    DB-->>API: Metadata Stored
    API->>K8s: Create Pipeline CR<br/>HTTPS 6443<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount Token
    K8s-->>API: CR Created
    API-->>OAuth: Pipeline Created Response
    OAuth-->>Route: Response
    Route-->>User: JSON Response<br/>Pipeline ID

    Note over User,MLMD: Flow 2: Pipeline Execution and Artifact Storage

    User->>Route: POST /apis/v2beta1/runs<br/>Create Pipeline Run
    Route->>OAuth: Validate OAuth
    OAuth->>API: Forward Request<br/>HTTP 8888
    API->>K8s: Create Workflow CR<br/>HTTPS 6443<br/>ServiceAccount Token
    K8s->>Argo: Workflow CR Created<br/>Controller watches CR
    Argo->>K8s: Create Workflow Pods<br/>HTTPS 6443
    K8s->>WorkflowPod: Pod Started<br/>Execute Pipeline Task

    WorkflowPod->>API: Get Pipeline Artifacts<br/>gRPC 8887<br/>ServiceAccount Token
    API-->>WorkflowPod: Artifact Metadata
    WorkflowPod->>Storage: Upload/Download Artifacts<br/>HTTP 9000 or HTTPS 443<br/>Access/Secret Keys
    Storage-->>WorkflowPod: Artifacts
    WorkflowPod->>MLMD: Log Artifact Lineage<br/>gRPC 8080<br/>Optional mTLS
    MLMD->>DB: Store Metadata<br/>MySQL 3306

    WorkflowPod->>WorkflowPod: Execute Task Logic<br/>Model Training/Data Processing

    Note over PersistAgent,DB: Flow 3: Metadata Persistence

    PersistAgent->>K8s: Watch Workflow CRs<br/>HTTPS 6443<br/>ServiceAccount Token
    K8s-->>PersistAgent: Workflow Status Updates
    PersistAgent->>API: Get Workflow Details<br/>gRPC 8887<br/>Bearer Token
    API-->>PersistAgent: Workflow Metadata
    PersistAgent->>DB: Persist Execution Metadata<br/>MySQL 3306<br/>Username/Password
    DB-->>PersistAgent: Metadata Stored

    WorkflowPod->>K8s: Task Complete<br/>Pod Terminated
    Argo->>K8s: Update Workflow Status<br/>HTTPS 6443
    PersistAgent->>DB: Update Final Status<br/>MySQL 3306

    Note over User,API: Flow 4: Metrics Collection

    User->>Route: GET /apis/v2beta1/runs/{id}<br/>Check Run Status
    Route->>OAuth: Validate OAuth
    OAuth->>API: Forward Request<br/>HTTP 8888
    API->>DB: Query Run Status<br/>MySQL 3306
    DB-->>API: Status + Metrics
    API-->>OAuth: Run Details
    OAuth-->>Route: Response
    Route-->>User: JSON Response<br/>Run Status + Artifacts
